{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story overview:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One dark night a child loses its dog. The next morning this child finds out that the dog has died. In grief over its animal companion's death the child ventures down to Necros, realm of the underworld, to find its dog and take it home again. On the childs adventure through the seven layers of Necros, it will meet cool friends, like the soulless robot Wacky, and fight bad guys, like the mean Dante.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will the child find its dog? or will the dark forces who also lurk in the underworld take their chance to rise to power? It's all in your hands! Or more like in your controller, or keyboard depending on what you use. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gravebond is a humorous, story focused experience that explores themes such as life, death, loss and meaning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">((Warning: Game contains imagery that may be harmful to players with photosensitive epilepsy or similar conditions.))</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn-based battles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Either defeat your enemies in traditional turn-based combat or gain their respect by guessing what will impress them </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies appear on map </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choices effects the ending </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No added sugar </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with charming characters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">May include a nice cat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect 35 hidden spirits </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 30 random events that differentiate between playthroughs </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At least one toilet joke </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nine differently themed worlds to explore </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eight alternative endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick and eat mushrooms </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Secret items and bosses </p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Enter the cave","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/467b244f76e007418f374d1a0d87a4be4d0fbd33.jpg"},{"name":"\u00dcber geil!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/3fc587f9d6486687724289793d61630972f38d1e.jpg"},{"name":"Bubble magic works!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/4d6cefb308258ef2c2d1b3edf5aa82a7ff78128d.jpg"},{"name":"A good deal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/6add7977d4f3c0b231fadf1ed2b7baff845bc42a.jpg"},{"name":"Bully the bully","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/7f0824e6946eb6ee36e1fd10fbf55cd9ab4fecf5.jpg"},{"name":"Origin of the statues","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/055d767c27f7c45eda2f89b6607a99c8b389c0ff.jpg"},{"name":"Conspiracy bird","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/9ba1ad967d3c54337614570bfdddb83a2fad25b6.jpg"},{"name":"Buff but intolerant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/215480d3d4e26a4dd2d72ed991c55f232be737d5.jpg"},{"name":"Snail eater!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/c1d629b67d08582893493541d514df60f953f2bf.jpg"},{"name":"Rock, paper, scissor master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2637180/7c00db3e72fa2d8537f22da61b3d0eef0fd894bc.jpg"}],"total":72},"background":"https://shared.ak